Instalace potřebných nástrojů

cross-AVR enviroment

== Gentoo

Install Gentoo cross development tools and build AVR cross-compile utilities.
GCC 4.4 seems be broken for AVR.

emerge sys-devel/crossdev
crossdev -t avr --g 4.2

== OpenSuSE

Add new repository with cross platform develoment tools from OpenSuse build 
service.

http://download.opensuse.org/repositories/CrossToolchain:/avr/openSUSE_11.3/

